    "text": "Technology Standards Task Force Act of 2021\n\nThis bill directs the Office of Science and Technology Policy to establish a task force on setting emerging technology standards, to be known as the Emerging Technology Standards-Setting Task Force.\n\nThe task force shall develop a long-term strategic plan for the United States to lead emerging technology standards-setting processes."
